{"sections":{"image_with_text_FEypfC":{"type":"image-with-text","settings":{"enable_section":true,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Golf.jpg","layout":"right","title":"Golf Hydration","text":"<p>BioSteel stands out as the perfect hydration solution for golfers seeking to maintain peak performance throughout their round. Golf demands sustained focus and physical endurance, often under challenging weather conditions. BioSteel's advanced electrolyte formula replenishes essential minerals lost through sweat, helping golfers maintain proper hydration and mental clarity from the first tee to the final putt. The balanced blend of sodium, potassium, and magnesium supports muscle function, reducing the risk of fatigue and cramping that can affect a golfer's swing mechanics and overall game.<\/p><p>What sets BioSteel apart on the golf course is its clean, natural ingredient profile. Free from artificial additives and excess sugars, BioSteel provides a steady source of energy without the crash associated with sugary sports drinks. This makes it ideal for maintaining consistent performance over a full 18 holes. The convenient powder mix format allows golfers to easily prepare their hydration drink on-demand, fitting perfectly into any golf bag. Whether facing a scorching summer tournament or a long day of practice, BioSteel's superior hydration support helps golfers stay focused, maintain proper form, and perform at their best when every stroke counts. By choosing BioSteel, golfers invest in a hydration strategy that aligns with the precision and endurance required in their sport.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":""}},"inf_collection_carousel_KQqfa4":{"type":"INF-CollectionCarousel","settings":{"use_background":false,"background":"#ffffff","heading":"Golf Hydration Mixes","heading_class":"h3","collection":"sports-hydration-mix","limit":12,"animation":"slide-up","animation--hover":"zoom","enable_button":false,"cta":"View Details","icon":"fa-arrow-right","padding_top":30,"pa